# The 32-piece granularity domain split

The single tracked source of the per-piece granularity constants. `GenExpVLit.lean` instantiates
and covers one `certDOverP`/`certDUnderP` pair per piece from this table, and `Floor/GranV` proves
the per-piece facts (`PieceOK`) over the same entries, so the generated covers and the proof
consume identical constants by construction.
-/

